data.description: The Birmingham III'a beautiful & classic ranch home! Vaulted great room/kitchen with beams! Today's open layout & decor is perfect for entertaining! Enjoy coffee or cocktails on the fully covered deck! Kitchen has granite island, upgraded appliances, huge walk-in pantry & custom cabinets. Hardwoods throughout living area, great room features beautiful gas fireplace. Master suite w/walk-in shower; granite & tile. D??cor features include upgraded fixtures, stunning designer touches. Taxes are estimated. Brookwood Farms is an active community with the Neighbor to Neighbor program providing lots of social activities for residents of all ages. Community pool & playground are open! Come see all that Brookwood Farms has to offer! Pictures are of previous model - finishes will vary. THIS HOME HAS MAIN FLOOR FINISH INCLUDED-BASEMENT FINISH IS OPTIONAL! 2021-10-29
